@startuml Manage Requests Flow

start

:Admin navigates to requests management page;

:Admin views list of all requests;

:Admin can filter by status, type;

:Admin selects a request to review;

:Admin views request details, pet/event info;

:Admin can approve or reject request;

if (Approve) then
  :Update status to approved;
  :Notify user;
  :Update pet status if applicable (e.g., adopted, claimed);
else if (Reject) then
  :Update status to rejected;
  :Add admin_notes;
endif

:Admin can add admin_notes;

:Submit, update record;

:Display success message;

stop

@enduml
